  "title": "A big star-like UFO sighted in Capão da Canoa-RS [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/28/a-big-star-like-ufo-sighted-in-capao-da-canoa-rs-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1ai",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 2nd, 1996</strong>. Time: 20h21. Duration: 4 minutes. From their home in the Santo Antonio region, in Capão da Canoa, State of Rio Grande do Sul, three people observed an unidentified flying object at an estimated distance of 40 km. According to the witnesses, the UFO had the appearance of a star, but &#8220;larger&#8221;; and it was amber in color and was at an altitude of approximately 1km. The unknown object was spotted when it flew in the western sector of the city Capão da Canoa. The sighting was carried out with the naked eye under a cloudy sky.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.434. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador em região não identificada”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
